snippet.title: Best VGM 779 - Beyond Good & Evil - Hyllian Suite
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube / PC / Xbox / PS2
Beyond Good and Evil (2003)
Hyllian Suite
Christophe Heral
